component.ts file will have @Component which has selector , TemplateUrl, styleUrl
example 
@Component({
selector: 'app-server',
templateUrl:'./app.component.html',
styleUrl:'./app.component.css';

we can have the inline templates and styles
Example:
@Component({
selector: 'app-server',
template: `<app-server></app-server>`
styles: [ `h1{
         color: "pink"
        }
        `]
styles is an array  as mentioned above. The inline template and style should be using using ` symbol.
